Homework 8 


8.1. Write a program to print the address of a variable whose value is input from user. 
8.2. Write a program to print the address of the pointer to a variable whose value is input 
from user. 
8.3. Write a program to print the value of the address of the pointer to a variable whose 
value is input from user. 
8.4. Write a program to print a number which is entered from keyboard using pointer. 
8.5. Write a function which will take pointer and display the number on screen. Take number 
from user and print it on screen using that function. 
8.6. Write a program to find out the greatest and the smallest among three numbers using 
pointers. 
8.7. Write a program to find the factorial of a number using pointers. 
8.8. Write a program to reverse the digits a number using pointers. 
8.9. Write a program to store n elements in an array and print the elements using pointer 
8.10. Write a program to Calculate the length of the string using a pointer 
8.11. Write a program to count the number of vowels and consonants in a string using a 
pointer 
8.12. Write a program in C to sort an array using Pointer
